data.description:
Welcome home! This beautifully maintained single family home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. With 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there is ample space for your family and guests to enjoy.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting interior that features a spacious split floor plan,  living room, formal dining, family room / Den, a cabana bathroom, and a breakfast nook which is the ideal spot to enjoy your morning coffee while soaking in the natural light. One of the standout features of this home is the converted garage, which adds an additional room and bathroom with private access. It's versatile and perfect for use as a guest suite, office, or even a rental space. If you ever need to revert it to a garage, it can easily be converted back to its original use.

The laundry room is incredibly spacious and comes equipped with a washer and dryer, both only a year old.

French doors with built-in blinds open up to the back patio, creating a seamless connection between indoor and outdoor living. Enjoy the serene and private backyard, complete with a screened in heated pool for year-round enjoyment and a large lanai which is perfect for entertaining guests. The fully fenced back yard includes a dog run fence, ensuring the safety of your furry family members.

For those with a green thumb, you'll appreciate the variety of fruit trees on the property, including orange, mango, pomelo citrus, and banana trees.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your own. It's a rare find with so much to offer, and it's waiting for you to call it home. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and Florida living
